  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span class=3DSpellE>Vodkol</span> is a powerful alc=
oholic
  beverage made from the roots of the <span class=3DSpellE>Vodia</span> pla=
nt.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>This hardy plant grows in the tundra wastelands of I=
ce
  worlds. Above ground the <span class=3DSpellE>Vodia</span> plant appears =
as a scraggly
  shrub with broad, pale yellow leaves. Below ground it has bulbous, white
  roots. </p>
